wikipedia_page.main: Alexander Mark Titchiner (born 13 June 1991) is a retired Welsh  footballer who last played for Flint Town United, as a striker.

response: The 2013/14 season was tougher, with Albion finding themselves in the relegation zone for most of the season. However a good run of form inspired by club favourite Alex Titchiner the club managed to finish 16th.
Alex Titchiner left the club after the 2011-12 season to join League Two side Fleetwood Town, rejoining in 2014.
